  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is the proof of concept study with multi-modality approach (using intra-thecal bioactive
      peptides, stem cells, laser and transcranial IV laser and Median Nerve stimulation as
      adjuvants) in cases of brain death due to traumatic brain injury having diffuse axonal injury
      to document possibility of reversal of brain death (BD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
